{"tid":1716140,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"手足唔該唔好再搞狗巴","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:57:22.000Z","uid":305160,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4353bda8ce8baabc299e8511152a2f53ced51749","tid":1716140,"uid":305160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:19:22.000Z","msg":"屋企藍絲表示唔明點解要搞狗巴<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/13/171018_282ca5b6d067d04606d88bc769886083.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F13%2F171018_282ca5b6d067d04606d88bc769886083.png&h=9ef953dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/13/171022_4b325619f01d0c7cd1a81bcfc691fd9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F13%2F171022_4b325619f01d0c7cd1a81bcfc691fd9e.png&h=a94e4e88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/13/171025_ca90a52dea64c133229a871f4637941b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F13%2F171025_ca90a52dea64c133229a871f4637941b.png&h=16997c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔敢話係咪手足做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋晚都見到手足有搞狗巴<br />\n但係好快就有其他手足制止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足真係唔好搞狗巴啦好失民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n雖然D深藍都冇得救<br />\n但中立同淺黃真係會唔明我地做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">利申：沙田柚</span>"},{"pid":"ecfadd9c2ed15849189ad5e14ce3fd432c700672","tid":1716140,"uid":293698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ab5c746e7d971ad0911a9a94e3b59d4c7f9281a","tid":1716140,"uid":42740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"咁都叫中立同淺黃?<br />\n選擇性搵野黎鬧 你見唔見佢有用同樣力度鬧黑警?<br />\n佢對於黑警既解釋又受唔受落? 唔受落又有冇繼續狙擊?<br />\n既然無既 你點解唔用返一樣既解釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4d095584d71d50287b307e85fb9c8ae26947e0","tid":1716140,"uid":305160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ab5c746e7d971ad0911a9a94e3b59d4c7f9281a","tid":1716140,"uid":42740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"咁都叫中立同淺黃?<br />\n選擇性搵野黎鬧 你見唔見佢有用同樣力度鬧黑警?<br />\n佢對於黑警既解釋又受唔受落? 唔受落又有冇繼續狙擊?<br />\n既然無既 你點解唔用返一樣既解釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"中立淺黃唔係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢擺明深藍啦<br />\n但問題係 佢見到搞狗巴吖嘛<br />\n都要講番點解有人搞狗巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然講講下發現佢都唔係同我講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d1fdd06ef8f2d7bed1cc6b517f0bda46d558f4","tid":1716140,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"攪狗巴咪攪狗巴，唔打司機就得"}]}